<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            /* max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto; */
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            padding: 10px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: left;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header img {
            width: 50px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #047857;
            margin: 0 0 0 15px;
        }

        .body {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .welcome-message p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lahri/image/upload/v1726333240/disax/tnbbn9m9vpueskb66qd3.png"
                alt="Climate Wavers Logo">
            <h1>Welcome Aboard</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="body">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <p>We're excited to have you join our community. Climate Wavers is your reliable platform for staying
                    informed
                    about crucial notifications, disaster alerts, and other important updates.</p>

                <p>Here’s what you can expect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Real-time Alerts:</strong> Receive up-to-date notifications directly from trusted
                        sources.</li>
                    <li><strong>Custom Notifications:</strong> Personalize the type of alerts you want to receive,
                        ensuring you're always informed about what matters to you.</li>
                    <li><strong>Safe and Secure:</strong> Your data privacy is our top priority, and we make sure all
                        information is securely handled.</li>
                </ul>

                <p>To get started:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Complete Your Profile:</strong> Fill in your basic details so we can tailor
                        notifications to your location and preferences.</li>
                    <li><strong>Set Your Preferences:</strong> Choose the types of alerts you'd like to receive — from
                        HR notices to disaster warnings.</li>
                    <li><strong>Stay Connected:</strong> Make sure your notifications are turned on so you never miss an
                        important message.</li>
                </ul>

                <p>We’re here to support you every step of the way. If you need any help, don't hesitate to reach out to
                    our support team.</p>

                <p>Welcome aboard! We look forward to helping you stay informed and prepared.</p>

                <p>Warm regards,<br>
                    The Climate Wavers Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>